{"tid":765731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【呃Like賺錢】網紅爸騙子女吃瀉藥雪糕 拍肚瀉如廁喊樣賺錢","createTime":"2018-08-03T04:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T05:29:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4cb1a1edd5998e5c7cde5468e544d79f24f7d1","tid":765731,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180803/_2018080311183618890.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180803%2F_2018080311183618890.jpg&h=100f77fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">布雷迪將瀉藥混入雪糕給其兒子及女兒進食。 網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n近年YouTuber大行其道，為了突圍而出和增加點擊率賺錢，不少網友會無所不用其極。美國內華達州一名YouTuber便利用「整蠱子女」的行為來幫自己提高頻道的點擊率。該名父親將瀉藥混入雪糕之中，再給其子女吃。最後其兒子及女兒因不停肚瀉而狂哭，狀況可憐。該名父親指下子女的肚瀉短片，上載至個人頻道，還命名為「我的天，這孩子的肚子壞了！」，影片被網民炮轟，上周YouTube暫停他的頻道，該條短片亦已被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n該名29歲父親布雷迪（Cordero James Brady）的頻道名為「DJ SO COOL」，有560萬追隨者。從影片可見，布雷迪將混了瀉藥的雪糕給其兒子及女兒進食，一個多小時後，孩子們隨即大叫，喊著向爸爸說「我肚子痛」。布雷迪拍下此情景，更笑說「我的天，這孩子的肚子壞了！」，之後他更走入洗手間，指下子女痛苦如廁的過程。兩名小孩哭著叫爸爸不要拍攝，邊瀉邊哭，他們更一度企圖關上廁所門，阻止爸爸拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n據當地警方表示，短片相信在2016年拍攝，當時警方與兒童保護部門聯合調查後，認為事件屬刑事案件，並已將報告呈交檢察官。不過，未知最後布雷迪有沒有被檢控。網站「<a href=\"http://babe.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbabe.net&d=YfP17A7Yj0qoJlgEaz2Hty7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=eccd3d17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">babe.net</a>」向YouTube舉報和投訴，上周YouTube終將短片刪除。<br />\n<br />\n反虐兒組織「Bulldog Solution」創辦人皮格蘭（Kortney Peagram）怒斥布雷迪虐兒，批評他這種傷害孩子行為，根本是危害兒童安全，「他正在示範及以鼓吹不當行為&hellip;&hellip;，他正教導自己的孩子傷害其他人沒有問題。」<br />\n<br />\n據知，布雷迪的頻道已賣給廣告商，只要越多人觀看廣告，他便可賺更多的錢。布雷迪頻道，主要是「惡搞片」，當中有玩弄孩子及自己伴侶的影片，如欺騙伴侶兒子遇溺死亡；在子女的房間燃點煙花，拍攝他們受驚走避情況等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180803/_2018080311122534407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180803%2F_2018080311122534407.jpg&h=0dbed4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一個多小時後，孩子們隨即肚瀉。 網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/781897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F781897&d=YfP17A7Yj0qoJlgEaz2Hty7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=05638a17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F781897&h=1dd849dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/781897</a>"},{"pid":"012ffe0a621936b4bd19042cd9592d3bb2803669","tid":765731,"uid":52215,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n邊到忍心咁樣對自己小朋友"},{"pid":"607d7d7a9a90ca154fc804198befbcd83c44275c","tid":765731,"uid":40763,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"呢個年代究竟有幾多人冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cf32813fcf92f785b3bbf6336f97d92d315223","tid":765731,"uid":61271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"Youtuber 都係on撚9<br />\n拍埋啲狗屎垃圾賺錢"},{"pid":"83ffc8b44cf26b5c461221cdee3c76c68c88b65f","tid":765731,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"咁細個就有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9849f02c2ecb38d33db1ecd39ae340e6f24f5ef4","tid":765731,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"Sorry Sorry Sorry Sorry"},{"pid":"d33472d202f3d887034d87f365485f9a76b1b9a4","tid":765731,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"係玉樹臨風既整蠱專家"},{"pid":"80987765babd70643f3307526a11a582ddff394e","tid":765731,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl